# Anything that shouldn't be in a catalog (don't accidentally commit cloned skills)
skills/*/SKILL.md
skills/*/references/
skills/*/scripts/
skills/*/assets/

# My own skill subdirs ARE committed — only ignore the cloned-skill leftovers above.
!my-skills/**/*.md
!my-skills/**/*.sh
